best use of your money and really the best use of our time. We want to
be there for you for some of the larger projects and some of the more
complicated things that you want to do in the system and new features
that get introduced. We want to be able to work with you on those. But
we really want you to be self sufficient in the platform and not having
to be relying on us or really anybody else. Also for your organization,
we want to really focus on enhancing efficiency and productivity. This
really kind of comes down to the cost benefit analysis of the system.
